├─ cart.html
├─ checkout.html
├─ styles.css
├─ common.js
├─ favicon.ico
├─ LICENSE
├─ README.md
├─ .gitignore
└─ images/
```

---

## 🛠 Setup Instructions

1. Download or clone this repository.
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/flip-phone-resale.git
   ```

2. Open locally  
   - Double‑click `index.html` to open in your browser.  
   - Or use a local server (e.g., VS Code Live Server extension).

3. Deploy online  
   - Push to GitHub and enable GitHub Pages in repo settings.  
   - Or host on Netlify, Vercel, or any static web host.

---

## 🔑 Notes
- Ensure `favicon.ico` is in the root folder.
- Place your `logo.png` and product images inside the `images/` folder.
- Filenames must match exactly (case‑sensitive).
- Cart data is stored in LocalStorage — it will persist until cleared.

